name: SR-NASDAQ-2025-007

name: SR-NASDAQ-2025-003

name: SR-NASDAQ-2025-002
description: A proposed rule change to establish fees for Industry Members2 related to reasonably budgeted CAT costs of the National Market System Plan Governing the Consolidated Audit Trail for 2025.

name: SR-NASDAQ-2025-001
